{
  "video_id": "vGX3FA_rQq4",
  "title": "The fascinating secret lives of giant clams | Mei Lin Neo",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12685.0,
      "end_time": 15731.0,
      "text": "Back home, my friends call me nicknames,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15755.0,
      "end_time": 17988.0,
      "text": "such as \"The Giant Clam Girl,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18120.0,
      "end_time": 19295.0,
      "text": "\"Clam Queen,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19319.0,
      "end_time": 21555.0,
      "text": "or, \"The Mother of Clams.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21579.0,
      "end_time": 22930.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22954.0,
      "end_time": 25209.0,
      "text": "This is because every time I see them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25233.0,
      "end_time": 28494.0,
      "text": "I talk nonstop about giant clams all day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28518.0,
      "end_time": 29795.0,
      "text": "every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 30774.0,
      "end_time": 34596.0,
      "text": "Giant clams are these massive and colorful shelled marine animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34620.0,
      "end_time": 36268.0,
      "text": "the largest of its kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36777.0,
      "end_time": 38493.0,
      "text": "Just look at this shell."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40142.0,
      "end_time": 43313.0,
      "text": "The biggest recorded individual was four-and-a-half-feet long"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43337.0,
      "end_time": 45711.0,
      "text": "and weighed about 550 pounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45735.0,
      "end_time": 48992.0,
      "text": "That is almost as heavy as three baby elephants."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50266.0,
      "end_time": 54683.0,
      "text": "South Pacific legends once described giant clams as man-eaters"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54707.0,
      "end_time": 58708.0,
      "text": "that would lie in wait on the seabed to trap unsuspecting divers."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59191.0,
      "end_time": 62389.0,
      "text": "A story goes that a diver had lost his legs"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62413.0,
      "end_time": 65328.0,
      "text": "while trying to retrieve a pearl from a giant clam."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65895.0,
      "end_time": 67310.0,
      "text": "I thought, \"Really?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68258.0,
      "end_time": 69922.0,
      "text": "So out of curiosity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69946.0,
      "end_time": 72593.0,
      "text": "I did an experiment using myself as bait."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73130.0,
      "end_time": 74368.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74929.0,
      "end_time": 78669.0,
      "text": "I carefully placed my hand into the clam&#39;s mouth and waited."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79640.0,
      "end_time": 80330.0,
      "text": "Hmm ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80355.0,
      "end_time": 81755.0,
      "text": "I still have my hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82731.0,
      "end_time": 85451.0,
      "text": "It seems that these gentle giants would rather retreat"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85475.0,
      "end_time": 87560.0,
      "text": "and protect their fleshy bodies"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87800.0,
      "end_time": 88291.0,
      "text": "than feed on me."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88315.0,
      "end_time": 90697.0,
      "text": "So much for those killer clam myths!"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91778.0,
      "end_time": 94470.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the reality is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94494.0,
      "end_time": 97121.0,
      "text": "we are the giant clams&#39; biggest threat."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 97855.0,
      "end_time": 102410.0,
      "text": "Considered a delicacy throughout the Western Pacific and Indian Oceans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102650.0,
      "end_time": 104876.0,
      "text": "giant clams have been traditionally fished as seafood."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105614.0,
      "end_time": 109154.0,
      "text": "Fishermen are particularly interested in their adductor muscles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109178.0,
      "end_time": 112707.0,
      "text": "which are organs that hold the two shells together like a hinge."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 113536.0,
      "end_time": 114948.0,
      "text": "Just for their muscles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114972.0,
      "end_time": 117311.0,
      "text": "giant clams were almost hunted to extinction"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117335.0,
      "end_time": 120000.0,
      "text": "between the 1960s and 1980s."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121370.0,
      "end_time": 124557.0,
      "text": "Clamshells are also popular in the ornamental trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124581.0,
      "end_time": 126547.0,
      "text": "as jewelry and for display."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127115.0,
      "end_time": 128857.0,
      "text": "In the South China Sea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128881.0,
      "end_time": 132783.0,
      "text": "fishermen went out of their way to collect fossilized clamshells"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132807.0,
      "end_time": 135411.0,
      "text": "by digging through large areas of coral reefs."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135811.0,
      "end_time": 141166.0,
      "text": "These were later carved and sold as so-called \"ivory handicrafts\" in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141757.0,
      "end_time": 145421.0,
      "text": "Giant clams, dead or alive, are not safe from us."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 145445.0,
      "end_time": 146797.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a \"clamity!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 147245.0,
      "end_time": 151637.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152518.0,
      "end_time": 156553.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 157593.0,
      "end_time": 161219.0,
      "text": "With the spotlight on more charismatic marine animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 161243.0,
      "end_time": 163409.0,
      "text": "such as the whales and coral reefs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163433.0,
      "end_time": 167132.0,
      "text": "it is easy to forget that other marine life needs our help, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167552.0,
      "end_time": 172471.0,
      "text": "My fascination with giant clams got me started on conservation research"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172495.0,
      "end_time": 175738.0,
      "text": "to fill in the knowledge gaps on their ecology and behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176292.0,
      "end_time": 179684.0,
      "text": "One of the discoveries that we made was that giant clams could walk"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 179708.0,
      "end_time": 181113.0,
      "text": "across the seafloor."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182172.0,
      "end_time": 183694.0,
      "text": "Yes, you heard me right:"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 183718.0,
      "end_time": 184918.0,
      "text": "they can walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 185355.0,
      "end_time": 186548.0,
      "text": "To find out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 186572.0,
      "end_time": 188805.0,
      "text": "we placed numerous baby clams on a grid."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 188829.0,
      "end_time": 191727.0,
      "text": "Now watch what happens over 24 hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 196892.0,
      "end_time": 200654.0,
      "text": "We think that walking is important for getting away from predators"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 200678.0,
      "end_time": 202666.0,
      "text": "and finding mates for breeding."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202690.0,
      "end_time": 206743.0,
      "text": "While it can hard to imagine any movement in these enormous animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 206767.0,
      "end_time": 210251.0,
      "text": "giant clams up to 400 pounds can still walk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 210275.0,
      "end_time": 211983.0,
      "text": "they just move slower."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 213348.0,
      "end_time": 217735.0,
      "text": "During my PhD, I discovered more secrets about the giant clams."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 217759.0,
      "end_time": 220983.0,
      "text": "But there was something missing in my work."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221823.0,
      "end_time": 223772.0,
      "text": "I found myself asking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223796.0,
      "end_time": 227255.0,
      "text": "\"Why should people care about conserving giant clams?\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 227279.0,
      "end_time": 229128.0,
      "text": "other than myself, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 230753.0,
      "end_time": 234613.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235713.0,
      "end_time": 239875.0,
      "text": "It turns out that giant clams have a giant impact on coral reefs."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 240314.0,
      "end_time": 243673.0,
      "text": "These multitasking clams are reef builders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 243697.0,
      "end_time": 245472.0,
      "text": "food factories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 245496.0,
      "end_time": 247843.0,
      "text": "shelters for shrimps and crabs"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 247867.0,
      "end_time": 249690.0,
      "text": "and water filters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 249930.0,
      "end_time": 250444.0,
      "text": "all rolled into one."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 250966.0,
      "end_time": 252363.0,
      "text": "In a nutshell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 252387.0,
      "end_time": 254756.0,
      "text": "giant clams play a major contributing role"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 254780.0,
      "end_time": 257107.0,
      "text": "as residents of their own reef home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 257130.0,
      "end_time": 260233.0,
      "text": "and just having them around keeps the reef healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 261000.0,
      "end_time": 264111.0,
      "text": "And because they can live up to 100 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 264135.0,
      "end_time": 267505.0,
      "text": "giant clams make vital indicators of coral reef health."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 268870.0,
      "end_time": 271133.0,
      "text": "So when giant clams start to disappear from coral reefs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 271777.0,
      "end_time": 273774.0,
      "text": "their absence can serve as an alarm bell"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 273798.0,
      "end_time": 276820.0,
      "text": "for scientists to start paying attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 276106.0,
      "end_time": 278357.0,
      "text": "similar to the canary in a coal mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 278958.0,
      "end_time": 280901.0,
      "text": "But giant clams are endangered."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 281675.0,
      "end_time": 285161.0,
      "text": "The largest clam in the world is facing the threat of extinction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 285185.0,
      "end_time": 289715.0,
      "text": "with more than 50 percent of the wild population severely depleted."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 290423.0,
      "end_time": 294227.0,
      "text": "And the ecological benefits of having giant clams on coral reefs"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 294251.0,
      "end_time": 298762.0,
      "text": "are likely to continue only if populations are healthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 298786.0,
      "end_time": 301123.0,
      "text": "making their conservation paramount."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 301790.0,
      "end_time": 305417.0,
      "text": "So I stand here today to give a voice to the giant clams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 305441.0,
      "end_time": 308448.0,
      "text": "because I care a whole lot for these amazing animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308472.0,
      "end_time": 310590.0,
      "text": "and they deserve to be cared for."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 311423.0,
      "end_time": 314979.0,
      "text": "It is time for the giant clams to step out of their shells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 315300.0,
      "end_time": 319150.0,
      "text": "and show the world that they, too, can be the heroes of the oceans."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 319174.0,
      "end_time": 320388.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 320413.0,
      "end_time": 324566.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}